{"tid":668293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【旺角騷亂】陪審團商議兩天仍未有結果 明早繼續","createTime":"2018-05-17T13:13:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T14:12:39.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8cfd5a896b1dcb4c90fcc2db13613a6bbbd74a68","tid":668293,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T13:13:53.000Z","msg":"前年大年初二凌晨旺角發生騷亂，本土民主前線前發言人梁天琦等5人被控煽惑暴動及參與暴動等罪，9人組成的陪審團約於昨天上午11時半退庭，惟商議兩天至今晚九時仍未有結果，法官彭寶琴下令他們休息，明早繼續。<br />\n<br />\n陪審團在八時提出商議多一小時，指因正商議的事項有連貫性，惟當時已明言今晚不會有全部結果。<br />\n梁天琦早前已承認一項襲警罪及被還柙，他現仍面對一項煽惑暴動，以及兩項暴動，控罪指他於前年2月8日至9日期間，在旺角砵蘭街和亞皆老街參與暴動，並連同黃台仰非法煽惑於砵蘭街的在場人士參與暴動。<br />\n另外，被告李諾文和盧建民各面對一項暴動罪；林傲軒則被控非法集結和暴動兩罪；林倫慶則被控3項暴動罪。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180517/58202409\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180517%2F58202409&d=NE8Lr1bIN6vmzfkdjRnNrWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=cfe2855b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180517%2F58202409&h=5f2d67ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180517/58202409</a>"},{"pid":"e82a1724b101a74e3e3d6f5c93c314a759ddd695","tid":668293,"uid":35219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T13:15:12.000Z","msg":"咁多條罪咁多個被告 有排搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ed4396b05758aa19cbdceb0a6aee04fc1a2fbc8","tid":668293,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T13:15:32.000Z","msg":"陪審團否決權  Jury Nullification"},{"pid":"c2a3283fae22a3460a078e42bcd8d135c9e44ef0","tid":668293,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T14:12:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}